sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Command as /arckit.requirements
    participant VersionFile as VERSION file
    participant Template as requirements-template.md
    participant Output as ARC-001-REQ-v1.0.md
    
    User->>Command: Execute command
    Command->>VersionFile: Read ${CLAUDE_PLUGIN_ROOT}/VERSION
    VersionFile-->>Command: "2.8.3"
    Command->>Template: Load template
    Template-->>Command: Template with [VERSION] placeholder
    Command->>Command: Replace [VERSION] with "2.8.3"
    Command->>Output: Write populated template
    Output-->>User: Generated artifact
